2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a structured-output learning framework using deep neural networks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to solve a computer vision problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image and pose data. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with 3D human pose estimation, which is relevant to robotics applications.
